title: 11/26/2020 – Hour 2 – Tom Brady is cooked, FOX NFL sideline reporter Kristina Pink
itunes:title: 11/26/2020 – Hour 2 – Tom Brady is cooked, FOX NFL sideline reporter Kristina Pink
description:
Doug Gottlieb and Rob Parker fill in for Dan Patrick and debate whether or not Tom Brady is ‘cooked.’ They are joined by FOX NFL Sideline reporter Kristina Pink live from Dallas to preview the NFC East match-up between the Washington Football Team and Dallas Cowboys. Plus, can Baltimore fix their offense in time to make a run in the playoffs?
